叫支那之外<br />\n就係諗住做愛，sex，做愛，外遇，偷情，同人妻人夫做愛，亂倫， 強姦，迷姦，撿屍"},{"pid":"53380c966ec7a274bd7b4438d009c57ff38b832d","tid":683272,"uid":48624,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">GOALLLLLLL</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/133453_7922206a3da47609638d61969c1098b0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F133453_7922206a3da47609638d61969c1098b0.gif&h=821eaa11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da2d35f29c2bbe66d34ef040b2d20d911863eaa0","tid":683272,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"暗戀了30ni年"},{"pid":"aa079741474df3f23bc874d4303754dbac723df5","tid":683272,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:21:17.000Z","msg":"根本就係Av劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6256d0669afec32065c89f87f9b79aa1e63f6d","tid":683272,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fd66903f8ab9fe932b03c802ede96d111ced60f","tid":683272,"uid":91771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"睇完單新聞，竟然會諗起番號，睇來要戒J 了<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E3%81%BE%E3%81%95%E3%81%AE%E3%82%8A/dp/B00WQC1YF0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2F%25E3%2581%25BE%25E3%2581%2595%25E3%2581%25AE%25E3%2582%258A%2Fdp%2FB00WQC1YF0&d=3bx6tFPt1d4aR3eCtR1RLE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=dbeb0b51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E3%81%BE%E3%81%95%E3%81%AE%E3%82%8A/dp/B00WQC1YF0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032a59f174450e99f6692449afe070b31f8347d7","tid":683272,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:22:40.000Z","msg":"點解一定係小黃/王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b15391ef7caaca21ecfcbf01db82f315c4cda9c","tid":683272,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"所以話"},{"pid":"f551a219156fcb9e36088c9225e91de10d2ce306","tid":683272,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:13:26.000Z","msg":"條女都四十幾歲 個男嘅都仲要玩兩q台灣人真係好淫賤"},{"pid":"f04b741817980854f8803d189c3b809d500215ce","tid":683272,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一名人妻前年8月特地從中南部北上參加小學同學會，想見見30年不見的老同學，不料喝太多，竟被黃姓男同學帶往摩鐵沒戴套性侵2次，還拿她的錢付房費及車資。新北地院開庭時，黃男雖否認性侵，但法官考量女子指控始終一致，出庭哭泣幾近無法言語，且通過測謊，昨依兩次強制性交罪判黃男5年徒刑。<br />\n <br />\n判決指出，被害女子2016年8月得知30年未見的小學同學要開同學會，專程北上參加。同學們先在<span style=\"color: red;\">新北市</span>新莊區一家餐廳聚會，再到KTV續攤唱歌，結束時女子已酒醉，走路搖搖晃晃，招手攔計程車，要前往妹妹在新北的住處，此時黃姓、楊姓2名男同學因為順路也上車，途中女子頭暈嘔吐，不料黃男(45歲)竟在楊男下車後，要司機開往五股一家摩鐵。<br />\n<br />\n黃男下車時，拿女子的錢付車資及嘔吐的清洗費，接著攙扶女子進房間，強拉她上床脫衣褲意圖性侵，女子當下表示：「我要回家」並躲閃，但仍被黃男沒戴保險套性侵，之後黃男到浴室洗澡，不久又硬上女子，但兩次都很快結束。<br />\n                                                                                     <br />\n黃男性侵女子兩次後，扶著意識仍不太清醒的女子離開摩鐵，再攔搭計程車讓女子返回妹妹家，女子直到返家後，才慢慢回想起整個受辱過程，除了告訴同學會吳姓召集人，也在同學LINE群組留言：「開心的北上參加」、「或許有些時間是空白了，但我不是傻瓜，耳朵跟身體的記憶是很清楚」、「事實就是我被無理的對待『性侵』了」、「黃ＸＸ你無需道歉作秀，我不會原諒你」、「趁人之危的小人」、「還從我皮包抽鈔票付計程車清潔費、摩鐵夜渡資！」黃男則回應：「我欠你（被害人）一個道歉」、「我沒有性侵妳」。<br />\n<br />\n女子提告後，黃男雖辯稱沒跟女子發生性行為，但合議庭考量被害女子指證歷歷，且通過測謊，反而黃男面對被害女子、同學提出質疑，不但沒有積極、正面澄清及解釋，甚至被問到為何帶被害女子去摩鐵時，還與同學爆發肢體衝突，法官綜合相關事證，不採信黃男的說法，昨判他有罪。仍可上訴。（孫友廉／新北報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180529/640_8449256e55c49890463bd7248a7f711b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180529%2F640_8449256e55c49890463bd7248a7f711b.jpg&h=f5e4e149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180529/1362486/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180529%2F1362486%2F&d=3bx6tFPt1d4aR3eCtR1RLE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d4ec81b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180529%2F1362486%2F&h=827b3cce\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180529/1362486/</a></blockquote><br />\n所有話......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a7149a7423a2df6f497cfd8797d0615a39fe9a","tid":683272,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"45更年期啦嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782c746b675c51386d5ae29a8ffe0c8a33b675d8","tid":683272,"uid":134484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T11:59:05.000Z","msg":"未撳入嚟都已經估到係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}